La '''Mont de Sëuc''' ([[Ladin gherdëina|gherdëina]]: ''Mont Sëuc'', [[badiot]]: ''Mont Suc'', [[Ladin fascian|fascian]]: ''Mont Sousc'', [[tudësch]]: ''Seiser Alm'', [[talian]]: ''Alpe di Siusi'') ie na [[mont]] tla [[Dolomites]] danter i luesc de [[Urtijëi]], [[Ciastel (BZ)|Ciastel]] y [[Sëuc]] (na [[frazion (Talia)|frazion]] de Ciastel), da chëla che la à si inuem. La ie a n'autëza dai 1.680 ai 2.350 metri. Cun na spersa de 56 km² iela la majera mont de l'[[Europa]]. 

[[File:Autumn on the meadows of Seiser Alm with Saslong.jpg|miniatura|500px|[[Mont Sëuc]], la majra mont de l'Europa, de autonn dan l [[Saslonch]]. La ie a na autëza dai 1680 ai 2350 metri.]]

